main event: A small oval white object was seen in the sky near Waupun, Wisconsin, disappearing in 1-3 seconds.
interesting points: The object was observed at an elevation of 40 degrees., The observation lasted between 1 to 3 seconds., The flight path of the object was curved., Duration and speed suggested it could be an aircraft but data was insufficient for analysis., The report is a part of the US Air Force's Project Blue Book.
